Class CompanyRepDbMgr

java.lang.Object
CompanyRepDbMgr
public class CompanyRepDbMgr extends Object
Manages the list of CompanyRep objects and their persistence to and from CSV. This class is implemented as a singleton and provides methods to add, remove, retrieve, sort and filter company representatives.

    • add

      public boolean add(String id, String companyName, String department, String position, CompanyRepStatus repStatus, String passwordTxt)
      Adds a new company representative to the list. This method checks for null IDs and prevents duplicate IDs.
      Parameters:
      id - company representative ID
      companyName - company name
      department - department
      position - position or title
      repStatus - approval status of the representative
      passwordTxt - plain-text password to be hashed and stored
      Returns:
      true if the representative was added, false if the ID is null or already exists
